---
import ChapterLayout from '../../layouts/ChapterLayout.astro';

const sections = [{"id":"definitie","label":"Definiție"},{"id":"tipuri","label":"Tipuri de grafuri"},{"id":"formule","label":"Formule"},{"id":"reprezentare","label":"Reprezentare"},{"id":"parcurgeri","label":"Parcurgeri"},{"id":"speciale","label":"Grafuri speciale"},{"id":"demo","label":"Demo interactiv"},{"id":"bac","label":"Probleme BAC"}];
---
<ChapterLayout
  title="Teoria Grafurilor"
  subtitle="Capitolul 12 — Grafuri neorientate și orientate, formule, parcurgeri, componente conexe"
  icon="🕸️"
  gradient="linear-gradient(135deg,#2e1065 0%,#581c87 50%,#9333ea 100%)"
  tags={["Grafuri","BFS","DFS","Matrice adiacență","Componente conexe","Graf complet"]}
  sections={sections}
  chapterNum={12}
  description="Teoria Grafurilor — informatică pentru liceu și bacalaureat"
>

<!-- ─── 1. DEFINIȚIE ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="definitie">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-purple">🕸️</span>
      <h2>Ce este un graf?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="beginner-box">
        <div class="bb-title">🌐 Analogie: Grafuri = Rețele</div>
        <p>Imaginează-ți o rețea de drumuri între orașe:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fiecare <strong>oraș</strong> este un <strong>nod</strong> (sau vârf)</li>
          <li>Fiecare <strong>drum</strong> dintre două orașe este o <strong>muchie</strong> (sau arc)</li>
          <li>Dacă drumul e cu sens unic → <strong>graf orientat</strong></li>
          <li>Dacă poți circula în ambele sensuri → <strong>graf neorientat</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Definiție formală:</strong> Un graf G = (V, E) este o pereche formată din:
        <ul>
          <li><strong>V</strong> = mulțimea <em>vârfurilor</em> (nodurilor), |V| = n</li>
          <li><strong>E</strong> = mulțimea <em>muchiilor</em> (arcelor), |E| = m</li>
        </ul>
        O muchie este o pereche &#123;u, v&#125; (neorientat) sau (u, v) (orientat) cu u, v ∈ V.
      </div>

      <!-- SVG: Basic graph illustration -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 200" width="400" height="200" style="max-width:100%;" aria-label="Graf neorientat cu 5 noduri">
          <!-- Edges -->
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="200" y2="40" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="120" y2="160" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="320" y2="70" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="200" y2="150" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="120" y1="160" x2="200" y2="150" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="150" x2="320" y2="70" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <!-- Nodes -->
          <circle cx="80" cy="60" r="18" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
          <text x="80" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">1</text>
          <circle cx="200" cy="40" r="18" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
          <text x="200" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">2</text>
          <circle cx="320" cy="70" r="18" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
          <text x="320" y="75" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">3</text>
          <circle cx="120" cy="160" r="18" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
          <text x="120" y="165" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">4</text>
          <circle cx="200" cy="150" r="18" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2.5"/>
          <text x="200" y="155" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">5</text>
        </svg>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;">G = (&#123;1,2,3,4,5&#125;, &#123;(1,2),(1,4),(2,3),(2,5),(4,5),(3,5)&#125;) — n=5, m=6</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;margin-top:14px;">
        <div class="card purple">
          <strong>Adiacență</strong>
          <p>Două noduri sunt <em>adiacente</em> dacă există o muchie între ele. Muchia este <em>incidentă</em> cu ambele noduri.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card blue">
          <strong>Gradul unui nod</strong>
          <p>Numărul de muchii incidente. La graf orientat: grad interior (d⁻) + grad exterior (d⁺).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 2. TIPURI DE GRAFURI ─────────────────────────── -->
<section id="tipuri">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-blue">📐</span>
      <h2>Tipuri de grafuri</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;margin:14px 0;">
        <div class="card blue">
          <strong>Graf neorientat</strong>
          <p>Muchiile nu au sens: &#123;u,v&#125; = &#123;v,u&#125;</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card green">
          <strong>Graf orientat (digraf)</strong>
          <p>Arcele au sens: (u,v) ≠ (v,u)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card purple">
          <strong>Graf ponderat</strong>
          <p>Fiecare muchie are un cost/greutate w(u,v)</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin:20px 0 12px;">Graf complet K<sub>n</sub></h3>
      <p>Un graf în care <strong>orice două noduri</strong> sunt adiacente (există muchie între oricare pereche).</p>

      <!-- SVG: Complete graphs K3, K4, K5 -->
      <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:16px 0;">
        <!-- K3 -->
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 120 110" width="120" height="110" aria-label="Graf complet K3">
            <line x1="60" y1="15" x2="20" y2="90" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="60" y1="15" x2="100" y2="90" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="90" x2="100" y2="90" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="60" cy="15" r="12" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="60" y="19" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">1</text>
