            <line x1="30" y1="115" x2="10" y2="50" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <circle cx="65" cy="10" r="11" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="65" y="14" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">1</text>
            <circle cx="120" cy="50" r="11" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="120" y="54" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">2</text>
            <circle cx="100" cy="115" r="11" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="100" y="119" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">3</text>
            <circle cx="30" cy="115" r="11" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="30" y="119" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">4</text>
            <circle cx="10" cy="50" r="11" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="10" y="54" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="var(--text)">5</text>
          </svg>
          <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-muted);">K₅ — 10 muchii</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin:20px 0 12px;">Subgraf și graf parțial</h3>
      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;margin:14px 0;">
        <div class="card orange">
          <strong>Subgraf</strong>
          <p>Se obține din G prin <strong>eliminarea unor noduri</strong> (și a tuturor muchiilor incidente cu ele). G' = (V', E') cu V' ⊆ V.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card teal">
          <strong>Graf parțial</strong>
          <p>Se obține din G prin <strong>eliminarea unor muchii</strong> (nodurile rămân toate). G' = (V, E') cu E' ⊆ E.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SVG: Subgraph vs Partial graph -->
      <div style="display:flex;gap:32px;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:16px 0;">
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:6px;">Graf original G</div>
