      <h2>Reprezentarea grafurilor în C++</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:10px;">1. Matrice de adiacență</h3>
      <p>a[i][j] = 1 dacă există muchia (i,j), 0 altfel. Spațiu: O(n²).</p>
      <pre><span class="kw">int</span> a[<span class="nu">101</span>][<span class="nu">101</span>], n, m;

<span class="cm">// Citire graf neorientat</span>
fin >> n >> m;
<span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nu">1</span>; i &lt;= m; i++) &#123;
    <span class="kw">int</span> x, y;
    fin >> x >> y;
    a[x][y] = a[y][x] = <span class="nu">1</span>;  <span class="cm">// neorientat: simetric</span>
&#125;

<span class="cm">// Grad nod v:</span>
<span class="kw">int</span> grad = <span class="nu">0</span>;
<span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> j = <span class="nu">1</span>; j &lt;= n; j++)
    grad += a[v][j];  <span class="cm">// O(n)</span></pre>

      <h3 style="margin:16px 0 10px;">2. Liste de adiacență</h3>
      <p>Pentru fiecare nod, o listă cu vecinii săi. Spațiu: O(n + m).</p>
      <pre><span class="kw">int</span> n, m;
vector&lt;<span class="kw">int</span>&gt; adj[<span class="nu">101</span>];  <span class="cm">// liste de adiacență</span>

fin >> n >> m;
<span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nu">1</span>; i &lt;= m; i++) &#123;
    <span class="kw">int</span> x, y;
    fin >> x >> y;
    adj[x].push_back(y);
    adj[y].push_back(x);  <span class="cm">// neorientat</span>
&#125;

<span class="cm">// Gradul nodului v = adj[v].size()</span>
<span class="cm">// Vecinii: for (int vec : adj[v]) ...</span></pre>

      <h3 style="margin:16px 0 10px;">3. Lista de muchii</h3>
      <pre><span class="kw">struct</span> Muchie &#123; <span class="kw">int</span> x, y, cost; &#125;;
Muchie edges[<span class="nu">10001</span>];

<span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nu">1</span>; i &lt;= m; i++)
    fin >> edges[i].x >> edges[i].y >> edges[i].cost;</pre>

      <div class="callout warning">
        <strong>Când folosim ce?</strong>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Matrice</strong>: n ≤ 100, accces rapid a[i][j] în O(1), grad ușor de calculat</li>
